ivardefs.name: code
ivardefs.desc: An error code,from a specified code system, which details why the claim could not be adjudicated.

ivardefs.name: detailSequenceLinkId
ivardefs.desc: The sequence number of the addition within the line item submitted which contains the error. This value is omitted when the error is not related to an Addition.

ivardefs.name: sequenceLinkId
ivardefs.desc: The sequence number of the line item submitted which contains the error. This value is omitted when the error is elsewhere.

ivardefs.name: subdetailSequenceLinkId
ivardefs.desc: The sequence number of the addition within the line item submitted which contains the error. This value is omitted when the error is not related to an Addition.
